meta {
  name: 8 Ask - safe refusal (no documents)
  type: http
  seq: 8
}

post {
  url: {{baseUrl}}/ask
  body: json
}

headers {
  X-Clinician-Id: {{clinician}}
}

body:json {
  {
    "patient_id": "patient-with-no-documents",
    "question": "What is this patient's latest cholesterol?"
  }
}

docs {
  A patient with no ingested documents must produce a labeled refusal, never
  an invented answer.

  -> 200 with degraded=true, empty citations, and an explicit "no documents
  are available" answer. The routing[] still shows the full supervisor loop -
  the graph ran and decided it had nothing grounded to say.
}
